r />\n<br />\n香港警員當晚在機場為遭示威者包圍的中國籍男子解圍時，一度因為被示威者襲擊而拔槍警告。之後，港警速龍小隊增援，驅散部分示威者並制服數人，這名中國籍男子才被送醫急救。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:05:38.000Z","msg":"唔出奇, 狗隊已經敗壞到極點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T22:05:59.000Z","msg":"十幾年前世貿韓農事件，已經好仆街<br />\n果時有名俾大家叫&rdquo;香港之恥&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n估唔到依仲仆街"},{"pid":"ea13f9812c215f51c84a4f600fb884fbd0591c40","tid":1586913,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fe80ca2844e6de1bce46c881ef093403a28d7c4","tid":1586913,"uid":130797,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:26:04.000Z","msg":"呢d就係用黎做國際文宣既材料<br />\n<br />\n但如果拎黎同狗講道理<br />\n結果就好似走入去動物園同d馬騮講道理一樣<br />\n激氣既只會係自己<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T22:26:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0783034be8030e227a1989c9d74144ce309f1d07","tid":1586913,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T22:44:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死黑警</span></span>"},{"pid":"16abc11a4558665ae787b608d9cc0cc9a99eb9f9","tid":1586913,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c22852882988c7807111d785db6a2c9a5f016860","tid":1586913,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"077bf37def2597e5bd5a77d36d0498d384b696ab","tid":1586913,"uid":282350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9506eaca61881c1ea4287a5be6ce30efaec1b7b","tid":1586913,"uid":71341,"like":1,"dislike":63,"score":-62,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:22:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:34:15.000Z","msg":"台灣唔係殖民地黎喎，係經歷過一段日治時期囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T21:47:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T23:02:14.000Z","msg":"殖民既意思唔係咁解架喎，同對方買武器就當殖民地，咁大陸要當係俄羅斯殖民地喎"},{"pid":"6575f6cd4ee26b04fcf86392ddb7bd45c2d8e71f","tid":1586913,"uid":289055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ae9742fde2380d2c4bd3163